---
title: Double Golden Cheesy Tomato Chicken with Baked Potatoes & Mayo
description: Keep your chicken tender and full of flavour by cooking them in a rich tomato sauce and covering the whole thing with Cheddar.
With a melted, gooey top and a colourful salad on the side, this chicken dinner will win over the whole family!
